summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from West Seattle General Hospital Corporation and others to a portion of the NE 1/4 of Section 36, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M., and other properties for street purposes and laying off 22nd Ave. Southwest, Southwest Elmgrove Street, South Barton Street, Northeast 120th Street, 12th Ave. Northeast and 14th Ave. Northeast.
